fullplot: For over 100 years Oxford and Cambridge have squared off once a year in a boxing match. This is the story of the Oxford blues that made the team in 2005.

title: Blue Blood

tomatoes.consensus: A crude comedy with nothing new or insightful to say about the subjects it satirizes.
